  "texts": [
    "Even as e-commerce companies work on the technology and infrastructure to enable drone-based delivery, citizens are concerned about on how their privacy will be impacted once it sees wide deployment.",
    "Clearly, much needs to be done to abate these concerns, in the form of governmental regulation and enforcement methods.",
    "Privadome is a step in that direction.",
    "Privadome can be integrated with city-scale regulatory authorities that oversee drone operations.",
    "It allows citizens equipped with a mobile phone to determine if their footage is recorded by drones in their vicinity, and request an audit trail from those drones to determine if they are privacy compliant."
  ],
